bandwidth-bi-threshold.help: Apply FEC parameters when available bi-bandwidth is >= threshold (kbps, 0 means no threshold).
bandwidth-bi-threshold.name: bandwidth-bi-threshold

bandwidth-down-threshold.help: Apply FEC parameters when available down bandwidth is >= threshold (kbps, 0 means no threshold).
bandwidth-down-threshold.name: bandwidth-down-threshold

bandwidth-up-threshold.help: Apply FEC parameters when available up bandwidth is >= threshold (kbps, 0 means no threshold).
bandwidth-up-threshold.name: bandwidth-up-threshold

latency-threshold.help: Apply FEC parameters when latency is <= threshold (0 means no threshold).
latency-threshold.name: latency-threshold

packet-loss-threshold.help: Apply FEC parameters when packet loss is >= threshold (0 - 100, 0 means no threshold).
packet-loss-threshold.name: packet-loss-threshold

results.help: Configure Forward Error Correction (FEC) mapping profiles.
results.name: fec
